{"tid":1628231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人，反抗] 今日和理非，最緊要人多","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T02:49:28.000Z","uid":74642,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8148abd41b4732ba9989912c22124a522dfcfc9","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"今日和理非回合，係表達緊我地重有好多人唔會屈伏喺禁蒙面法底下，我地唔會中林鄭計，逆轉民意，今日主線唔會破壞，係重申訴求<br />\n<br />\n無論你覺得前線做得好唔好，我地核彈都唔割，今日正正係話比政府同所有市民聽，個運動重有幾多人支持<br />\n<br />\n如果今日係多人，我地可以繼續行落去，如果係少人，好快就比林鄭騎劫民意分化和理非同佢地口中嘅暴徒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分和勇，今日兩點見</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b6bd6571f1e1c2622291b7645b829125079749e","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"不分和勇，今日兩點見"},{"pid":"1045c641bd08b71f6a94217d0386e384d5a93afd","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"不分和勇，今日兩點見"},{"pid":"878128477fed6f40501e208ccf9a461cf7d175e0","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"叫你身邊嘅人一齊出黎"},{"pid":"fb41362314037219dc81d5b038d748389ae52573","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:43:10.000Z","msg":"不分和勇，今日兩點見"},{"pid":"9c3dfd9ce08f629f9ff1b743f2edcdc4a306a6d3","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"不分和勇，今日兩點見"},{"pid":"62d802cccabb642e50274e8973554f4de48fe2ae","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"319bdff60f94c1b263eb603a36b159d4b96ad645","tid":1628231,"uid":148082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:43:33.000Z","msg":"一陣見"},{"pid":"51e013e5ec625d67a849365b90781c11c79c0042","tid":1628231,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":